// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0281 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 869ea4e9-d83c-53b3-b932-75c8b8ad7b66

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:5.0*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:24.10*")
